---
layout: base
permalink: /index.html
title: 'Beep...Boop...you made it!'
description: 'Eleventy starter using modern CSS, fluid type, fluid spacing, flexible layout and progressive enhancement.'
blog:
  title: 'Blog'
  intro: "Here are the 4 most recent posts. There's probably more though..."
---

<div class="wrapper">
  <header class="full | section" style="--spot-color: var(--color-primary)">
    <div class="section__inner flow region">
      <h1 class="text-center" style="color: var(--color-bg);">{{ title }}</h1>
    </div>
    {% svg "divider/pixels", null, "divider" %}
  </header>

  <article class="full | region">
    <div class="wrapper flow prose">
      <h2 id="an-eleventy-starter">I'm Kyle!</h2>
      <p>I'm an IT professional working in the MSP/Cybersecurity industry. I love everything tech. You can check out more about me <a href="https://profile.kylereddoch.me">here</a> or read my blog posts below. I blog about cybersecurity, technology trends, and best practices in IT. I even share the occasional tech review every now and then.</p>
{% highlight "bash" %}
$ hostname
cyberseckyle.local

$ cat about-$(hostname).config
description = "Cybersecurity analyst and MSP operator focused on securing modern infrastructure. Lover of all things tech and coffee."
focus_areas = ["Endpoint Hardening", "Network Security", "Threat Intelligence", "Cloud Security"]
tech_stack = ["PowerShell", "Python", "Linux", "SonicWall", "Kaseya", "EDR/XDR", "SIEM"]

$ diagnostics --run full
> Scanning system configs... ✅
> Verifying patch compliance... ✅
> Reviewing firewall rules... ⚠️  minor gaps found
> Checking audit logs... ✅
> Correlating threat intel... ✅

Report saved to /opt/kyle/intel/summary-2025-07-30.log

$ buildtime
{{ helpers.buildTime() }}
{% endhighlight %}
    </div>
  </article>

  <section class="full | region">
    <div class="wrapper flow prose">
      <h2>{{ blog.title }}</h2>
      {% if blog.intro %}
        <p>{{ blog.intro }}</p>
      {% endif %}
      <div class="feature |  region region-space-l">
        <custom-masonry layout="50-50">
          {% set itemList = collections.allPosts %}
					{% asyncEach item in itemList.slice(0, 4) %}
            {% set headingLevel = "h3" %}
						{% include "partials/card-blog.njk" %}
					{% endeach %}
        </custom-masonry>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

    <div class="wrapper flow">
      <p style="text-align: center;"><a href="/blog/">View more posts</a></p>
  </div>
</div>
